The expert reviews confirm the implementation is solid. Key findings:

**All features working correctly:**
- `repairOcrText` called in all 4 required places (single, 2-line join, 3-line join, caps-coalescing)
- OCR substitution map covers all plan-specified cases (Í handled implicitly via `.toLowerCase()`)
