{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01HD9pFYNEvAs27STgXEc8Eo","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Review complete. Here's the summary:\n\n**Tests**: 33/33 passed. CLI outputs match pre-change baseline (no regressions).\n\n**Issues found and fixed**:\n1. **Array notation violations** — 4 places used `T[]` instead of `Array<T>` (AGENTS.md requirement). Fixed.\n2. **Redundant `--` pattern** — `/^--\\s*\\w/` was in both `METADATA_PATTERNS` and `passesHardFilters`. Removed the duplicate from `passesHardFilters` since `looksLikeMetadata()` already covers it.\n\n**Key verification**: The substring deduplication logic (\"keep the shorter\") is untouched. The compound-title guard is a short-circuit `return true` that fires *before* the dedup logic, preventing compound titles from being subject to it at all.\n\n**Overall**: Clean implementation that faithfully follows the improvement plan. All 11 changes from the plan are present and correctly implemented. Performance is fine — dictionary lookup is O(1), substitution generation is bounded, and the embedding call remains the dominant cost. Review written to `tools/title-loop/docs/24-b15aa30/review.md`."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1597,"cache_read_input_tokens":54461,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1597},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ec54b805-2592-4abe-8e4f-4011b51bb626","uuid":"34851834-1d5e-4bc2-a3df-46e1c34a2006"}
